<pre>
<b>Date:</b>           Fri, 10 Apr 1998 20:05:06 -0400
<b>From:</b>           "George B. Bush" &lt;<a href= 
"mailto:twixt@cstone.net">gbbush@rockbridge.net</a>&gt;
